"CodePipeline orchestrates the entire CI/CD workflow,
CodeBuild handles compilation testing and Docker image creation,
CodeDeploy handles the actual deployment to EC2, EKS or Lambda with
rolling or blue/green strategies"


Think of it like:

CodePipeline = Manager
               coordinates everything
               tells who does what

CodeBuild    = Builder
               compiles code
               runs tests
               creates artifact

CodeDeploy   = Deployer
               takes artifact
               deploys to EC2/EKS/Lambda
---
Full flow:

Developer pushes code to Git
        │
        ▼
CodePipeline triggers    ← orchestrator
        │
        ▼
CodeBuild runs           ← builder
├── mvn clean install
├── run unit tests
├── build docker image
└── push to ECR
        │
        ▼
CodeDeploy deploys       ← deployer
├── pull from ECR
├── deploy to EC2
├── deploy to EKS
└── deploy to Lambda

---

CodePipeline — Orchestrator:

What it does:
├── Connects all stages together
├── Source → Build → Test → Deploy
├── Triggers automatically on code push
└── Manages the entire workflow

Example stages:
Stage 1 → Source    (CodeCommit/GitHub)
Stage 2 → Build     (CodeBuild)
Stage 3 → Test      (CodeBuild)
Stage 4 → Deploy    (CodeDeploy)
Stage 5 → Approval  (manual gate)
Stage 6 → Prod Deploy (CodeDeploy)
------------------

CodeBuild — Builder:

What it does:
├── Compiles source code
├── Runs unit tests
├── Creates build artifacts
├── Builds Docker images
└── Pushes to ECR/S3

Config file → buildspec.yml:
version: 0.2
phases:
  install:
    commands:
      - pip install -r requirements.txt
  build:
    commands:
      - mvn clean install
      - docker build -t myapp .
  post_build:
    commands:
      - docker push myapp:latest
-------------

CodeDeploy — Deployer:

What it does:
├── Deploys to EC2 instances
├── Deploys to ECS/EKS
├── Deploys to Lambda
├── Rolling deployments
├── Blue/Green deployments
└── Automatic rollback on failure

Config file → appspec.yml:
version: 0.0
os: linux
files:
  - source: /
    destination: /var/www/myapp
hooks:
  AfterInstall:
    - location: scripts/restart.sh
  ValidateService:
    - location: scripts/health-check.sh
-------------------------------------------------
